metadata.name: NaughtyPups Club #1
metadata.description: Aaaaarrr RuuUUUFFF! NaughtyPups Club is a collectible NFT project centred around naughty puppies...WOOF WOOF. Puppies can also be cute and kind so we decided that 50% of ALL Royalties (forever) will go back to the puppy loving community via giveaways, competitions and event; so keep barking as loud as you can because we want everyone to win!
